<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000136> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A fat-storing cell found mostly in the abdominal cavity and subcutaneous tissue of mammals. Fat is usually stored in the form of triglycerides." .
