_:B9318859eb08c6fd5e35b24dc8f8cc631 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedSource> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0011822> .
_:B9318859eb08c6fd5e35b24dc8f8cc631 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedProperty> <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> .
